The Congress of South African Trade Unions National May Day rally will be in Nelson Mandela Bay Metro at Isaac Wolfson Stadium and will be addressed by the President of COSATU S”dumo Dlamini, President of the ANC Cyril Ramaphosa, General Secretary of the SACP Cde Blade Nzimande and SANCO President Cde Richard Mdakane. COSATU celebrates the 2018 May Day under the theme: “Building Unity and Cohesion of COSATU to advance the National Democratic Revolution. Attached is a list of other COSATU May Day celebrations all across the country. For security purposes at the National May Day event, members of the media are encouraged to apply for accreditation at: Xolani@cosatu.org.za or monethilerato@gmail.com